metadata.name: The Wait
metadata.description:
This piece puts you in a trance between waiting and patience, we are all on earth waiting for the second coming of our saviour or a transition to a higher power.

“Time stands still as an anticipation and uncertainty mingle in the heart of the patient, waiting for the moment when all will be revealed.”

I put myself into a trance to evolve through this process as time comes to a pause but not a definite stop.
